    rcpp_count_mers

    rcpp_count_mers.Rd

    returns count all mers

    Arguments

    aavector

    StringVector [mandatory]

    ncores

    number of cores [default: 1]

    Value

    list

    Author

    Kristian K Ullrich

    Examples

    ## load example sequence data
data("hiv", package="MSA2dist")
h <- hiv |>
    MSA2dist::subString(s=1, e=12) |>
    MSA2dist::cds2aa() |>
    as.character()
l <- korthoR::rcpp_count_mers(
    aavector=h,
    ncores=1)
#>
